        "Episode number 5 of Series \"Religions of the world\". The program covers the characteristics and origins of Hinduism, a religion with no single founder and no defined organisation. Hinduism is an ancient path in the modern world with roots that stretch back before the dawn of recorded time. The program also looks at how the caste system operates as part of Indian society."
